<h1 id="biography">Biography</h1>

<p>I am a Project Scientist working with Professor <a href="//www.michaelfranz.com/" target="_blank">Michael Franz</a> at the <a href="//www.ics.uci.edu/" target="_blank">Donald Bren School of Information and Computer Science</a> at <a href="//www.uci.edu" target="_blank">UC Irvine</a>.</p>

<p>I co-founded <a href="https://www.immunant.com" target="_blank">Immunant, Inc.</a> a startup focusing on <a href="https://www.c2rust.com" target="_blank">language migration</a> and <a href="https://github.com/immunant/selfrando" target="_blank">exploit mitigation</a> to protect systems software against malicious inputs.</p>


    <div class="row">

      
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <h3>Interests</h3>
        <ul class="ul-interests">
          
          <li><a href="https://www.c2rust.com" target="_blank">Language Migration</a></li>
          
          <li>Compilers</li>
          
          <li>Exploit Mitigation</li>
          
          <li>Information Security</li>
          
        </ul>
